n Walsh。 （对于那些不认识的人，博士后职位是一种低薪炼狱，当他们无法立即获得教授工作时，有博士学位的人会继续进行研究。）沃尔什是<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Taking-America-Back-Conservative-Movement/dp/0300260970">最近发布</a>的<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Taking-America-Back-Conservative-Movement/dp/0300260970">书《</a><em>把美国带回来：保守派运动和最右边</em>，但他在Twitter上最著名的是声乐和备受瞩目的评论员。当我的播客联合主持人布拉德·德隆（Brad DeLong）<a href="https://x.com/delong/status/1100157177816379395">在2019年宣布</a>，现在是像他这样的新自由主义者将警棍“传递给同事”的时候了，他引用了沃尔什（Walsh）的一条推文。近年来，沃尔什（Walsh）花了很多时间从左边攻击乔·拜登（Joe Biden）。自加沙战争开始以来，这些攻击变得更加艰难。</p><p>但这不是今天在一个tizz味中获得Twitter的原因 - 或X。取而代之的是，沃尔什（Walsh）宣布他未能获得终身任职的学术工作至少是由于他是白人的事实： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:go